{"tid":2505894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陸委會：香港越嚟越似大陸","createTime":"2021-04-27T03:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T03:35:08.000Z","uid":125168,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d39d545aa2b86cf78d2ffdfbaef12dac64a00751","tid":2505894,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:17:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210426/5PFAWT2JOBHD7G5PIZ6Z243RJE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210426%2F5PFAWT2JOBHD7G5PIZ6Z243RJE%2F&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B62CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=be8bb218\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20210426%2F5PFAWT2JOBHD7G5PIZ6Z243RJE%2F&h=2324c9d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20210426/5PFAWT2JOBHD7G5PIZ6Z243RJE/</a><br />\n<br />\n近日港人發現，從香港伺服器無法登陸台灣基督長老教會網站、民進黨及國防部國軍人才招募中心的網站。陸委會今（26日）表示，我方呼籲相關方面應確保香港民眾「知的權利」，勿一再高築、擴張網路長城，否則終將自損香港的國際形象與世界金融中心地位。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會指出，資訊自由是基本人權，也是香港作為國際城市的重要基石。<span class=\"red\">相關方面閹割香港資訊自由的作為，只會對外釋出香港愈益近似中國大陸之訊號。</span><br />\n<br />\n此前，2月香港多個網路供應商都無法連接促轉會官網，包括數碼通、香港寬頻、香港電訊、3電信及中國移動等網路供應商，均顯示「無法連線至此網站」，只能透過VPN經德國、美國等海外國家的伺服器才能登入。香港保安局當時同樣表示，對任何針對警方執法行動的揣測不作評論。（陳建瑜／台北報導）"},{"pid":"0b15e86f3e586cc9e2a6d52ff90f375bf3b352f1","tid":2505894,"uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf5fb92254664b18e993f53370b9e2378b67fcd","tid":2505894,"uid":50386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0b15e86f3e586cc9e2a6d52ff90f375bf3b352f1","tid":2505894,"uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:20:28.000Z","msg":"PR響前面救火<br />\n政府響後面淋火水<br />\n點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s